text: ao anakneasar( mou ham meat). chaur anak phdal nouv avei delke ban banhchouh aoy anak pi mcheasa robsa anak . te brasenbae anak min thveu te noh ku anak minban phdal sar robsa trong laey . haey a l laoh nung roksaa anak pi( tongveu akrak) mnoussa lok . pitabrakd nasa a l laoh min changaoulobangheanh champoh krom del brachheang laey
